<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contact-us.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nav-bar-white.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Footer.css">
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="../CSS/support.css"> -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
     <!-- BootStrap -->
     <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/css/bootstrap.min.css"> -->
    <script src="/Javascript/contact-us.js"></script>
    <script src="/Javascript/nav-bar.js"></script>
    <title>Contact Us | Customer Care | Firoza</title>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('./partials/Nav-bar.ejs') %>

    <section class="CU">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Contact Us</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="main">
            <a href="/user/contactUsform" id="Contact-us" class="main-content">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa-regular fa-file-lines"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="main-text-content">
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>Send us a message and ask us to contact you</p>
                </div>
            </a>
            <!-- <a href="" id="CSAI" class="main-content">
                <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="main-text-content">
                    <h3>Personal customer support attendant</h3>
                    <p>Ask our special customer support AI any question you want</p>
                </div>
            </a> -->
            <a href="mailto:ww.cs@Firoza.com" id="Email-us" class="main-content">
                <div id="email-us-row">
                    <div class="icon">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope-open"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="main-text-content">
                        <h3>Email Us</h3>
                        <p>Our Firoza ambassadors will gladly respond to your requests</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="drop-down">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down" id="arrow-down"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-up" style="display: none;" id="arrow-up"></i>
                </div>
                <div id="email" style="display: none;">
                    <p class="main-text-content" id="cs-email-address">ww.cs@Firoza.com</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="FAQ">
        <div class="title">
            <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="FAQ-container">
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>What is Firoza?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Firoza is a distinguished jewelry brand dedicated to celebrating diverse cultures from around the globe.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>How can I make a purchase from Firoza?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>To make a purchase on our website, you must register for an account.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>What is your return policy?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>We accept returns and exchanges depending on the reason and the time elapsed since the purchase was made.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>Is it possible to cancel my order?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Yes, orders can be canceled as long as they have not yet been shipped.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>What shipping options do you provide?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>We offer both expedited and standard shipping options.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>Where does Firoza operate?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Currently, we operate exclusively in the Middle East and Africa.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>What inspires Firoza?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Our brand is inspired by the rich and diverse cultures from around the world.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>Do I need an account to make a purchase?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Yes, an account is required to complete a purchase on our website.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="FAQ-item">
                <div class="question-button-div">
                    <h2>Can I change my shipping address after placing an order?</h2>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <p>Yes, you can update your shipping address before the order is shipped by contacting our customer support team.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>    
    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>